# Boundless FC - Project Memory

## Project Overview
- **Name**: Boundless FC
- **Type**: Single-page marketing + operations site for international grassroots futsal community
- **Stack**: Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind v4, shadcn/ui v4 (base-nova)
- **Budget**: $0 (Vercel Hobby + Supabase Free Tier)

## Design System (STRICTLY FOLLOW)

### Colors (All Tokenized)
| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--background` | `#151F2B` | Main dark background (all sections except shop) |
| `--foreground` | `#FAEAC2` | ALL text, headings, nav links |
| `--primary` | `#FF6C47` | Orange wine - subheaders, prices, CTA buttons (sessions/tournaments) |
| `--primary-foreground` | `#FAEAC2` | Text on primary buttons |
| `--secondary` | `#DB856A` | Light orange - subheaders in hero/about |
| `--accent` | `#FAEAC2` | Gold accent - buttons, highlights |
| `--accent-foreground` | `#151F2B` | Dark text on accent buttons |
| `--border` | `#FAEAC2` | Full opacity border |
| `--border-subtle` | `rgba(250, 234, 194, 0.3)` | 0.3 opacity borders (tokenized) |

### CRITICAL RULES
- **NO WHITE ANYWHERE** - `#FFFFFF` removed from design system
- **Font**: Inter ONLY - no Oswald, no display font
- **All colors MUST be tokenized** - no hardcoded hex in components
- **Borders**: Use `border-border-subtle` (0.3 opacity) for all borders

### Shop Section Exception
- Background: `#FAEAC2` (light cream)
- Text: `#151F2B` (dark)
- Prices: `#FF6C47` (orange wine)
- "Place Order" buttons: Dark background, light text

